        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Greedy/mission_raccoon/scene_raccoon_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository a23f4ad5-6857-4501-a53d-53522a671b88).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to the JPMorgan Chase bank, home to over $3.8 trillion worth of assets, $1.4 trillion of that being part of the worlds largest money laundering scheme. The objective is simple, kill the undercover heads of the laundering ring with a pistol to show that M13Delta can be anywhere, anytime. Oh, and snap the neck of the bank CEO and take as much from the vault as you like, since she stiffed the bill on The Romainian Job.",
